00:02:16.199 --> 00:02:19.840
This is the account where some of Jesus' disciples

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:24.199
chose to leave everything behind and follow him.

00:02:24.199 --> 00:02:25.719
Here's the setting.

00:02:25.719 --> 00:02:28.800
Some of Jesus' disciples were fishermen

00:02:28.800 --> 00:02:31.520
