00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:39.960
and move them to follow him fully.

00:02:39.960 --> 00:02:41.960
So what did he do?

00:02:41.960 --> 00:02:45.520
He used a powerful object lesson

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:48.479
that provided a point and a purpose.

00:02:48.479 --> 00:02:50.919
Let's read it at Luke chapter one

00:02:50.919 --> 00:02:55.560
or five rather, verse one through verse 11.

00:02:55.560 --> 00:02:57.919
And look for the point, first of all,

00:02:57.919 --> 00:03:00.080
behind what Jesus did here.

00:03:01.240 --> 00:03:05.479
It says on one occasion when the crowd was pressing in on him

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:07.960
and listening to the word of God.

00:03:07.960 --> 00:03:10.840
He was standing by the lake of Ganesirat,

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:14.000
and he saw two boats docked at the lakeside,

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.759
but the fishermen had got out of them

00:03:15.759 --> 00:03:18.240
and were washing off their nets.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:21.199
Going aboard one of the boats, which was Simon's,

00:03:21.199 --> 00:03:24.039
he asked him to pull away a bit from land.

00:03:24.039 --> 00:03:27.800
Then he sat down and he began teaching the crowds

00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:29.280
from the boat.

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:32.159
When he stopped speaking, he said to Simon,

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:33.919
pull out to wear it as deep

00:03:33.919 --> 00:03:37.000
and let down your nets for a catch.

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:39.120
But in reply, Simon said,

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:42.759
instructor, we toiled all night and caught nothing.

00:03:42.759 --> 00:03:45.599
But at your word, I will lower the nets.

00:03:45.599 --> 00:03:47.400
Well, when they did this,

00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:49.319
they caught a great number of fish.

00:03:49.319 --> 00:03:52.840
In fact, their nets began ripping apart.

00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:54.560
So the emotion to their partners

00:03:54.560 --> 00:03:56.599
and the other boat to come into system,

00:03:56.599 --> 00:03:58.840
and they came and filled both boats

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:01.560
so that these began to sink.

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:04.599
Seeing this, Simon Peter fell down at the knees

00:04:04.599 --> 00:04:07.520
of Jesus saying, to part from me, Lord,

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:10.159
because I'm a sinful man.

00:04:10.159 --> 00:04:13.159
For both he and those with whom were overwhelmed

00:04:13.159 --> 00:04:16.959
with astonishment at the catch of fish, they had taken.

00:04:16.959 --> 00:04:20.040
Man, the same was true of both James and John,

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:23.480
Zebedee's sons, who were partners with Simon.

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:27.360
But Jesus said to Simon, stop being afraid.

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:31.120
From now on, you will be catching men alive.

00:04:31.120 --> 00:04:33.560
So they brought the boats back to land

00:04:33.560 --> 00:04:37.680
and abandoned everything and followed him.

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:44.000
So what was the point behind this miracle here?

00:04:44.759 --> 00:04:46.160
What was this?

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:48.839
Their needs would be cared for

00:04:48.839 --> 00:04:52.839
if they trusted in Jesus and followed him.

00:04:52.839 --> 00:04:56.600
Of course, to do this, they had to believe Jesus, didn't they?

00:04:56.600 --> 00:04:57.639
They had to listen to him.

00:04:57.639 --> 00:04:59.639
This was not a trick.

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:03.160
With their own eyes, they could see that catch of fish

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:06.160
and then deduce that their needs would, in fact,

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:07.959
be cared for by Jesus.

00:05:07.959 --> 00:05:09.759
That was the point.

00:05:09.759 --> 00:05:11.160
Did they get it?

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:13.439
Yes, they did, with what result?

00:05:13.439 --> 00:05:17.000
Well, it says they were moved to abandon everything

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:19.319
and follow Jesus.

00:05:19.319 --> 00:05:21.720
That is, everything related to the fishing business.

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:25.079
They gave it all up and followed him.

00:05:25.079 --> 00:05:29.199
Almost instantly, their faith and trust in Jesus grew,

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:30.839
didn't it?

00:05:30.839 --> 00:05:33.720
Now, let's bring the point up to our day.

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:37.199
Soon, you will go to your assignments.

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:40.680
Will you remember the point of your gilly training?

