never forget the point and the purpose behind the blessing

00:08:37.879 --> 00:08:42.039
that you just experienced in being part of this class.

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:44.519
Trust in Jehovah and in his Son

00:08:44.559 --> 00:08:46.720
to help you at all times

